{"tid":1982444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【玩大佢】中國憲法規定國家由工人階級領導，林鄭冇做過工人，違反憲法","createTime":"2020-04-21T08:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T04:35:55.000Z","uid":48040,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e2418cb3d6f90746da6de12e6b4054b4693359a0","tid":1982444,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"港共政府問責團隊違反了中國憲法，應該全部下台。<br />\n我求其搵個工人來做特首都好過佢。<br />\n<br />\n中國憲法第一條：中華人民共和國是<span style=\"color: red;\">工人階級領導</span>的、以工農聯盟為基礎的人民民主專政的社會主義國家。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n借位宣傳，我地係新創立的Youtube Channel 「思想加」，用動畫方式分享社會學理論，每週一集：<br />\n<br />\n第一期：國家如何綁架我們的社會？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cLRI-zP7UZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcLRI-zP7UZ4&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c25641fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cLRI-zP7UZ4</a><br />\n<br />\n第二期：背棄「社會契約」的政府，也必將被人民拋棄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Wq9lQZA_Xc&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=f670ba3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc</a>"},{"pid":"ba39eef06c005890b751a4ba9dae7940cb476080","tid":1982444,"uid":165749,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"特別行政工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b83233f0045b780c1777c77585d2c27e884bbd","tid":1982444,"uid":79410,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"成個憲法都呃9人"},{"pid":"0ff33059eac9ef9b1098c9158257b4c207bd6ffb","tid":1982444,"uid":48040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"82b83233f0045b780c1777c77585d2c27e884bbd","tid":1982444,"uid":79410,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"成個憲法都呃9人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"對，但維尼同李克強當年的確